      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CORNHILL WARRIOR (2) struggled to get involved last start at this track, but prior to that won by 1.3 lengths at Ballarat (22.34) beating Blame Margaret in a T3 RSTW on May 23. Should bounce back. SWEET MILLIE (6) was quickly into stride and burnt early from the middle draw where she gave a sight, finishing third (24.30) and beaten 3.5 lengths over 425m at this track. Bold showing expected. ABRACADABRA (4) jumped from out wide and had a clear run, crossing to the lead and holding on for a placing when third (23.34) at Warragul in a Grade 5 over 400m. Will give a great sight again. PAW EDEN (1) is not to be discarded.",
